<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019814>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 36–40. Genitalia of Atheta aemula (Erichson) (male (36–39) and female (40), 1.5–2.5 km N Lawrence, Kansas). 36 — median lobe, parameral view; 37 — apex of median lobe, parameral view; 38 — median lobe, lateral view; 39 — apex of median lobe, lateral view; 40 — spermatheca. Scale bar 0.1 mm (37, 39), 0.2 mm (36, 38, 40)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5019814/files/figure.png" .

